# 👨‍💼 JobPathway – Android Career Guidance App

**A modern Android app to help users explore career paths, understand required skills, and prepare effectively for their future.**

JobPathway provides a guided experience for students and job seekers to explore various professions, assess their strengths, and get suggestions for skills and learning paths. Built using **Kotlin**, **Android Jetpack**, and **RoomDB**, the app offers a sleek UI and offline-first functionality tailored for Indian users.

---

## 📱 Features

- 🔍 Career path suggestions based on user input
- 🧠 Skill recommendations & self-assessment
- 📄 Setup & manage user profiles
- 🔒 Secure login & onboarding screens
- 💾 Offline support with RoomDB
- 🎨 Clean Material Design interface

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer          | Tech                        |
|----------------|-----------------------------|
| Language       | Kotlin                      |
| Architecture   | MVVM, Jetpack Components    |
| Database       | RoomDB                      |
| UI Design      | XML, Material Design        |
| IDE            | Android Studio              |

